1606:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-boot/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * 2. Since the FIFO is shared between 2 USIC channels, FIFO size should be carefully selected. A F
1607:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-boot/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * event is generated when the FIFO filling level falls below the \a limit value.
