1789:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-boot/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * Writes data to the transmit FIFO in frame length control mode. \n\n
